Date: Fri, 29 Oct 2021 19:05:41 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] asus/am1i-a: update the ACPI routing to match the new IRQ routing

Update the ACPI routing in accordance with the new IRQ tables.

Signed-off-by: Mike Banon <mikebdp2@gmail.com>
Change-Id: I4901c96acafeba279104ff3fb10cacc7b5693d37
---

